### Login as Admin (Run this first, copy the returned token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

> {% client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.token); %}

### Login as Analyst
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "analyst",
  "password": "analyst"
}

> {% client.global.set("analyst_token", response.body.token); %}

### Login as Viewer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "viewer",
  "password": "viewer"
}

> {% client.global.set("viewer_token", response.body.token); %}

### Create an Income Record (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/records
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 1000.50,
  "type": "INCOME",
  "category": "Salary",
  "date": "2026-04-01T10:00:00",
  "description": "April Salary"
}

### Create an Expense Record (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/records
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 250.00,
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "category": "Groceries",
  "date": "2026-04-02T10:00:00",
  "description": "Weekly Groceries"
}

### Create Record as Analyst (Should Fail - 403 Forbidden)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/records
Authorization: Bearer {{analyst_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 500.00,
  "type": "INCOME",
  "category": "Freelance",
  "date": "2026-04-03T10:00:00",
  "description": "Freelance work"
}

### View All Records (Admin or Analyst)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/records
Authorization: Bearer {{analyst_token}}

### View Dashboard Summary (Available to ALL authenticated users)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}
